      "author": "Rumcajsev",
      "description": "## What's new\n\n- **Scroll-based heading highlighting now works in reading mode** — the sidebar highlights the heading matching your current scroll position in both edit/live-preview and reading mode\n- **Highlighting works with \"Nothing\" auto-expand mode** — previously, setting auto-expand to Nothing prevented highlighting from starting at all\n- **More reliable scroll detection** — fixed cases where the wrong editor pane was being tracked, causing highlighting to silently stop working",
