      "author": "Rumcajsev",
      "description": "Initial release of Navigate Headings for Obsidian.\r\n\r\n## Features\r\n- Expand files in the explorer to see heading structure\r\n- Click headings to jump to sections\r\n- Auto-highlight current reading position\r\n- Customizable heading depth and auto-expand levels\r\n- Smooth animations with indent guides\r\n- Compatible with Iconic and similar icon plugins\r\n\r\n## Installation\r\nExtract the release files into .obsidian/plugins/navigate-headings-in-files-explorer/ in your vault, then reload Obsidian and enable the plugin.\r\n\r\n## Requirements\r\n- Obsidian 1.0.0 or later\r\n- Desktop version (Mac, Windows, Linux)",
